headline: Micron earnings, Fed commentary: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Wednesday, December 17, including commentary from top Federal Reserve officials and earnings results from companies like Micron Technology (MU), General Mills (GIS), and Worthington Steel (WS). headline: Jobs Data, Inflation Report, Micron Earnings: Coming This Week
summary: The last full trading week before Christmas is looking busy. Key economic data that was delayed by the shutdown is due, including the jobs report and the consumer-price index for November. Some Federal Reserve policymakers are due to speak, after the central bank's latest rate cut last week, and a reasonably busy earnings calendar includes earnings from Nike, FedEx and Micron.
